<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Challenge Not Approved – OnlyFunds</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 20px; background: #f5f5f5; color: #333; }
    .email-container { max-width: 400px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); }
    .banner { width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .greeting { font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .title { color: #dc3545; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .challenge-type { color: #333; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: bold; }
    .description { color: #666; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .challenge-info { background: #fff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; border: 2px solid #dc3545; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .info-item { color: #333; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .info-value { color: #6c757d; font-weight: bold; }
    .observation { background: #fff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; border: 2px solid #007bff; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .observation-title { color: #6c757d; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .observation-content { color: #333; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.4; }
    .action-button { background: #007bff; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 20px; border: none; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; width: 100%; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; display: block; cursor: pointer; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .action-button:hover { background: #0056b3; color: #ffffff; }
    .footer { color: #666; font-size: 12px; text-align: center; }
    .company-name { color: #007bff; font-weight: bold; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    {{#if banner}}
    <img src="{{banner}}" alt="OnlyFunds Banner" class="banner" />
    {{/if}}

  <div class="greeting">Dear trader,</div>
    <div class="title">Challenge Not Approved</div>
    <div class="challenge-type">{{challengeType}} – ${{accountSize}}</div>
  <div class="description">We regret to inform you that your challenge has not been approved this time.</div>
    
    <div class="challenge-info">
      <div class="info-item"><strong>Status:</strong>
        <span class="info-value">Not Approved</span></div>
      <div class="info-item"><strong>Challenge Type:</strong>
        <span class="info-value">{{challengeType}}</span></div>
      <div class="info-item"><strong>Account Size:</strong>
        <span class="info-value">${{accountSize}}</span></div>
      <div class="info-item"><strong>Review Date:</strong>
        <span class="info-value">{{reviewDate}}</span></div>
    </div>

    {{#if observation}}
    <div class="observation">
      <div class="observation-title">Review Comments:</div>
      <div class="observation-content">{{observation}}</div>
    </div>
    {{/if}}

    <div class="description">
  Don't be discouraged! This is part of the learning process. We recommend:
  <br><br>
  • Reviewing your trading and risk management strategy<br>
  • Analyzing your performance during the challenge<br>
  • Considering starting a new challenge when you're ready<br>
  • Contacting our support team if you have questions
    </div>

    <a href="{{landingUrl}}/challenges" class="action-button" target="_blank">Start New Challenge</a>
    <a href="{{landingUrl}}/support" class="action-button" target="_blank">Contact Support</a>

    <div class="footer">
      Best regards,<br />
      <span class="company-name">OnlyFunds</span> Team
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>